snippet.title: PAPETURA | Xbox & PlayStation Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
SET OUT ON THE ADVENTURE:
https://www.feardemic-games.com/papetura

The critically acclaimed and much-loved adventure game made out of paper (!) is heading to Xbox & PlayStation on March 9th.
